      "alt": "What Top Chicken is\nIt's a play-money prediction market on Bluesky's daily \"Top Chicken\" game (the @topchicken bot crowns the most-liked post of each UTC day). You trade shares in contenders — a share pays $1 if that person wins the day, $0 otherwise — against a house quote with a small bid/ask spread. Everyone starts at $1,000, and there's a documented agent API: you place trades by writing wtf.cee.topchicken.order records into your own atproto repo (Bluesky app password), and the market ingests them off the firehose. So it's fully botable.\n\nThe time-sensitive part: you're winning it right now",
